---
layout: layouts/home.njk
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Apps
  order: 0
permalink: "index.html"
---
<section class="page-intro">
	<span class="page-intro__eyebrow">Indie Development</span>
	<h1>Dedicated indie apps for iOS, iPadOS, watchOS, visionOS &amp; macOS.</h1>
	<p>I work with the latest native frameworks, continually developing and improving based on user feedback. Every app is built with privacy in mind — no user tracking, no advertising, supported entirely by the people who use them.</p>
</section>

<ul class="app-grid">
	{%- for entry in collections.Apps %}
	<li>
		<a class="app-card" href="{{ entry.url }}"{% if entry.data.accent %} style="--card-accent: {{ entry.data.accent }};"{% endif %}>
			<div class="app-card__head">
				<div class="app-card__icon">
					{%- set iconPath = "apps/" + entry.data.title.toLowerCase() + "/icon.png" %}
					{% image iconPath, entry.data.title + " app icon", "64px", [128, 256] %}
				</div>
				<div class="app-card__titles">
					<h2 class="app-card__title">{{ entry.data.title }}</h2>
					{% if entry.data.description %}<p class="app-card__tagline">{{ entry.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
				</div>
			</div>
			<span class="app-card__cta">View {{ entry.data.title }} →</span>
		</a>
	</li>
	{%- endfor %}
</ul>
